    title: 'Who Is Jesus? What Scripture Actually Says',
    excerpt: 'The identity of Jesus Christ is the central question of human history. Discover what the Bible reveals about who He truly is.',
    date: 'Mar 13, 2026',
    category: 'Bible Study',
    readTime: '9 min read',
